| **Rate limiting** | `express-rate-limit` | Mitigates brute-force and scraping |
| **Input validation** | Parse & validate `page`/`limit` params | Prevents unexpected behavior from malformed input |
| **Error handler** | Global `(err, req, res, next)` middleware | Prevents stack trace leakage to clients |
| **404 handler** | Explicit JSON 404 | Hides Express version info from default HTML errors |
| **Port config** | `process.env.PORT` | Avoids hardcoded port; standard for deployment |

