| No body size limits | 🟠 Important | Add `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` |
| No CORS config | 🟠 Important | Add `cors` middleware |
| Timestamp in `/health` | 🟡 Best Practice | Remove or restrict |
| No input validation | 🟡 Best Practice | Use `zod`/`joi` for query/body params |

